headline: Quest Diagnostics (DGX): A Fresh Look at Valuation After Strong Q3 Earnings and Raised Outlook
summary: Quest Diagnostics posted higher third-quarter earnings and revenue, both topping market expectations and showing clear improvement from last year. The company also raised its full-year revenue outlook, which signals sustained business momentum. See our latest analysis for Quest Diagnostics. Quest Diagnostics’ robust third-quarter results have combined with a solid run for shareholders this year, as the stock’s year-to-date price return sits at an impressive 24.28%. headline: Oracle Names Stephen Rusckowski to the Board of Directors
summary: Oracle Corporation (NYSE: ORCL) today announced that it unanimously elected Stephen Rusckowski to Oracle's Board of Directors and increased the size of the Board to 14. The election is effective as of November 18, 2025.
